:"2017-06-03T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拓寬下圈子先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我由細到大都係女性絕緣體<br />\n上網識又驚識到mk妹同d 唔三唔四既人<br />\n不如你講d辦法俾我識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039681081eeb5c424dc0320c537320e1209026ab","tid":269162,"uid":120930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>師兄 令到自己sporty 先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有做gym嫁<br />\n不過玩極都大隻唔到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係操得唔夠啦<br />\n身體很誠實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點先為操得夠<br />\n其後我唸應該都夠<br />\n我一星期都有三日<br />\n只不過我重量去到某個位做唔上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ded971c6fb2f497b798486c97e27dddf07ea05","tid":269162,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>師兄 令到自己sporty 先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有做gym嫁<br />\n不過玩極都大隻唔到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係操得唔夠啦<br />\n身體很誠實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點先為操得夠<br />\n其後我唸應該都夠<br />\n我一星期都有三日<br />\n只不過我重量去到某個位做唔上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點樣操法呀<br />\n唔可能上唔到去架喎"},{"pid":"1b46c4927a44ee23bb032a19f9bb97879cb16dc1","tid":269162,"uid":120930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>師兄 令到自己sporty 先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有做gym嫁<br />\n不過玩極都大隻唔到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係操得唔夠啦<br />\n身體很誠實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點先為操得夠<br />\n其後我唸應該都夠<br />\n我一星期都有三日<br />\n只不過我重量去到某個位做唔上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點樣操法呀<br />\n唔可能上唔到去架喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做8-12下 每個動作4組<br />\n每次都上網搵下d新動作<br />\n通常都5個動作